data.description: Escape to spacious living! Step into this expansive home situated on nearly 2 acres, offering room to breathe and unwind. The main level features 3 generously sized bedrooms, while the kitchen boasts a convenient laundry closet suitable for a stackable unit. Additional space awaits in the walk-up attic, complete with its own bathroom. Discover the fully finished basement, a versatile haven featuring a small kitchen, family room, two additional rooms, and another bathroom and laundry area. The leveled yard, adorned with just the right amount of trees, strikes a perfect balance between privacy and openness. Outside, don't miss the sizable storage building and a charming garden area, enhancing the overall appeal of this property. Conveniently located just a few miles from the nearest I-81 exit, this spacious home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Seize the opportunity to make this your dream home!
